CHRISTMAS LIGHTS: DEXTROSE, CORN SYRUP, CITRIC ACID, CALCIUM STEARATE, TAPIOCA DEXTRIN, COLOR (TITANIUM DIOXIDE, RED #40, YELLOW #5, BLUE #1), CONFECTIONER'S GLAZE, CARNAUBA WAX.
